    - target: {fileID: 3381331621216345205, guid: ce1b2c84ccefa374787d1c62a2148e14, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<b>The Master Path</b>\nMemorize the path shown in the first zone of
        the Labyrinthine City.\n\n<b>The 90-Degree Rule</b>\nThe path remains identical
        in every zone but <b>rotates 90 degrees clockwise</b> as you move into each
        new quadrant.\n\n<b>Close the Loop</b>\nUse spatial reasoning to navigate
        all four zones. Completing the full square circuit breaks the sorcerer\u2019s
        spell.\n\n<b>Avoid Reality Collapse</b>\nStay strictly on the hidden path
        using <b>WASD</b>. Stepping into the abyss will trigger a \"reality collapse\"
        and reset your progress."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3381331621216345205, guid: ce1b2c84ccefa374787d1c62a2148e14, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_isRightToLeft
      value: 0
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3381331621216345205, guid: ce1b2c84ccefa374787d1c62a2148e14, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_TextStyleHashCode
      value: -1183493901
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8552350622531435229, guid: ce1b2c84ccefa374787d1c62a2148e14, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_Name
      value: Tutorial Box
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
